data.description: Don’t miss this well kept 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath two-story townhome with 1-car garage in Riverview Lakes. This spacious home boasts an open concept living space with soft, neutral finishes and low maintenance ceramic tile on the first floor. Full laundry room and powder room are located off the main living space. The large kitchen is well-equipped with a sizable pantry. Upstairs the master retreat features walk-in closets and en-suite bathroom with dual sinks and expansive vanity. Additional bedrooms are roomy with ample closet space. From the downstairs living area, step out your sliding glass doors and soak up the Florida lifestyle in the outdoor screened-in patio.This desirable gated townhome community includes a pier overlooking a beautiful lake and scenic walk along a wetland conservation trail. Easy access to I-4 and I-75 for easy commutes, with plenty of prime shopping and dining nearby. HOA conveniently includes all exterior maintenance such as lawn care, water and sewer. No CDD fee.
